OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777061157
OL,3,CMan cleared of dumping 50 hares
OL,4,Coutside village shop
OL,6,FA father-of-three has been found not
OL,7,Fguilty of causing criminal damage to a
OL,8,Fvillage shop by smearing the blood of
OL,9,Fa hare over the front door, but has
OL,10,Fbeen convicted of possessing two
OL,11,Fprotected birds.
OL,13,FJames Kempster, 39, who lives at a
OL,14,Fcaravan site in Totton, Southampton,
OL,15,Fwas on trial at Southampton
OL,16,FMagistrates' Court after 50 hares were
OL,17,Fdumped outside Broughton Community
OL,18,FShop in the early hours of March 15,
OL,19,F2024.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
