OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777061157
OL,3,CMan cleared of dumping 50 hares
OL,4,Coutside village shop
OL,6,FAdam Cooper, prosecuting, told the
OL,7,Fcourt CCTV footage showed three men
OL,8,Farrive in a car, with two men getting
OL,9,Fout and dumping the hares.
OL,11,FOne of the men, both of whom were
OL,12,Fwearing balaclavas, is then seen to
OL,13,Fsmear hare blood on the store front
OL,14,Fbefore stuffing a dead kestrel and a
OL,15,Fbarn owl under the door handles in
OL,16,Fwhat Mr Cooper described as a "horror
OL,17,Fmovie scene".
OL,19,FThe car was found burnt-out in a
OL,20,Fcountry lane after the incident, the
OL,21,Fcourt heard.
OL,26,@xD@_OUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
