OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777061157
OL,3,CMan cleared of dumping 50 hares
OL,4,Coutside village shop
OL,6,FThe magistrates found Kempster guilty
OL,7,Fof two counts of possessing a dead
OL,8,Fbird under the Wildlife and
OL,9,FCountryside Act.
OL,11,FThe prosecution said DNA from two
OL,12,Fpeople found on the owl was a billion
OL,13,Ftimes more likely to have come from
OL,14,FKempster and an unknown individual
OL,15,Fthan from two individuals not related
OL,16,Fto the defendant, with weaker DNA
OL,17,Fevidence linking him to the kestrel as
OL,18,Fwell.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
