OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777061157
OL,3,CMan cleared of dumping 50 hares
OL,4,Coutside village shop
OL,6,FKevin White, the chairman of the
OL,7,Fbench, said the DNA evidence proved
OL,8,Fthe defendant was in possession of the
OL,9,Ftwo birds at some point.
OL,11,FBut he said there was "insufficient
OL,12,Fevidence" to convict Kempster of being
OL,13,Fpresent at the time of the Broughton
OL,14,Fincident, explaining the trousers he
OL,15,Fwas wearing did not match CCTV footage
OL,16,Fof the defendant at a petrol station a
OL,17,Fday earlier.
OL,26,@sD@WOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
