OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777061157
OL,3,CMan cleared of dumping 50 hares
OL,4,Coutside village shop
OL,6,FThe magistrates ordered a pre-sentence
OL,7,Freport to be produced on Kempster and
OL,8,Fwarned him they are considering all
OL,9,Foptions, including custody, for the
OL,10,Ftwo offences, which carry a maximum
OL,11,Fpenalty of six months' imprisonment or
OL,12,Fa fine.
OL,14,FMr White told the defendant: "We need
OL,15,Fto know more about you and the
OL,16,Fcircumstances around these events.
OL,18,F"The more we understand, the more
OL,19,Flikely we are to give a sentence that
OL,20,Fis appropriate."
OL,26,@vD@^OUzD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777061157
OL,3,CMan cleared of dumping 50 hares
OL,4,Coutside village shop
OL,6,FGiving evidence, Kempster denied being
OL,7,Fthe man shown on the CCTV putting the
OL,8,Fhares in front of the shop and the two
OL,9,Fbirds under the door handles.
OL,11,FWhen asked what he was doing that
OL,12,Fnight, he said: "I can't remember last
OL,13,Fweek let alone two years ago."
OL,15,FWhen Mr Cooper asked the defendant how
OL,16,Fhis DNA was found at the scene,
OL,17,FKempster replied: "The only way I can
OL,18,Fexplain, it is transferrable DNA."
OL,20,FThe defendant also denied burning out
OL,21,Fthe car used in the incident.
OL,26,@tD@QOUuD@^O]yD@SOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777061157
OL,3,CMan cleared of dumping 50 hares
OL,4,Coutside village shop
OL,6,FKempster will be sentenced at the same
OL,7,Fcourt on June 23.
OL,9,FTest Valley rural inspector Stu Ross,
OL,10,Fof Hampshire Constabulary, said: "This
OL,11,Fwas a shocking incident which caused
OL,12,Fdistress to a small village community
OL,13,Fin the heart of rural Hampshire.
OL,15,F"The dumping of animal carcasses is
OL,16,Fsomething we see across the county and
OL,17,Fcan be used as an intimidation tactic
OL,18,Fby criminals operating in remote rural
OL,19,Fareas to taunt local people and create
OL,20,Fadditional misery.
OL,26,@rD@bOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
