FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777061157
OL,3,CMan cleared of dumping 50 hares
OL,4,Coutside village shop
OL,6,F"The sheer number of animals that were
OL,7,Fkilled and deposited outside the
OL,8,FBroughton shop on this occasion was
OL,9,Fappalling, and we simply will not
OL,10,Ftolerate our communities being
OL,11,Fterrorised in this manner."
